## TODO Management
- Unversioned TODOs are forbidden
- Format: `TODO[vX.Y]: description`
- Must include:
  - Target version
  - Brief description
  - Link to issue/ticket (if applicable)

Example:
```python
# TODO[v2.1]: Implement rate limiting for API calls
# Issue: #123
def process_api_request():
    pass
```

